<div class="dc"><div style="padding:1rem 1.5rem;border-bottom:1px solid #f1f5f9;font-size:.9rem;font-weight:700;color:#374151;"><i class="fas fa-building" style="color:#3282B8"></i> Department Breakdown</div>
